Cameron Van Hoy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cameron_Van_Hoy 0 Cameron Van Hoy (born May 21, 1985) is an American actor, producer and writer. He first came to attention as the protagonist of Pups (1999), a critically acclaimed indie crime drama. Cameron_Van_Hoy ( born May_21_,_1985 ) is an_American_actor_,_producer_and_writer .
